{"tid":1776282,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"叱咤我最喜愛歌曲一齊投俾莊正手足","createTime":"2019-12-09T12:01:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-10T15:13:53.000Z","uid":27764,"like":121,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":80,"replies":[{"pid":"d3a5b905a1c0dcc9fdca8fa064bcd6944cded491","tid":1776282,"uid":27764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T12:01:07.000Z","msg":"早兩日有人提過有位歌手係救poly果日被捕俾人告暴動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢首派台歌而家喺叱咤我最喜愛歌曲上面投緊票<br />\n我哋唔可以為佢做啲咩，大家唯一可以做嘅就係投票俾佢鼓勵佢，等佢知道好多人都支持佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我知道大家心目中有好多歌想投，但係依家只係揀十強，大家一齊推手足首歌等佢比更多人認識幫佢圓夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢首歌係佢出道第一首歌但係都好可能係最後一首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ErqNTmm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FErqNTmm.png&h=5a7de64c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n投票網站<br />\n<a href=\"https://usca.my903.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fusca.my903.com&d=qnVsOlgekcepRBzFpIlw%2F8TiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=b7bd8e40\" target=\"_blank\">https://usca.my903.com</a><br />\n<br />\n莊正 - 開放世界<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=A79kJfcbKeE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DA79kJfcbKeE&d=qnVsOlgekcepRBzFpIlw%2F8TiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=06204859\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=A79kJfcbKeE</a>"},{"pid":"7725431c0681e82e6ddf00d615ae70721aaf5d37","tid":1776282,"uid":27764,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T12:04:02.000Z","msg":"追夢，最終被控暴動。<br />\n還記得「Come on James」嗎？當年條片網上好紅，眨眼已經6年前。<br />\n他，就是當日的James。<br />\n他，因為救理大，而被控暴動。<br />\n他，叫做莊正。<br />\n好奇怪的人，他夢想係唱歌。14年參加歌唱比賽勝出。等了5年，夢想成真。Sony Music簽了他，今年終於成功有自己的一首歌，成為一個新人，未發生運動之前，他說「最興奮去頒獎禮」。<br />\n如果是你，夢想成真的一刻，應該會好好珍惜吧？<br />\n他沒有。<br />\n理大被警圍捕時，眾人前往營救，結果莊正被捕，被控暴動。<br />\n自己的夢可能已破碎，但他仍在想著他人「當時最擔心嘅，其實唔係自己，反而覺得對唔住要身邊嘅人擔心，會內疚」。<br />\n「如果想救我想幫我，堅持自己理念」他在被捕後這樣說，「五大訴求，缺一不可」。<br />\n夢醒了，他卻做回自己。比起娛樂圈中任何一個已成名，但背棄良知的人，更值得尊敬。<br />\n記住他，他是值得紅的人。<br />\nLester 莊正<br />\n<br />\nFrom: 家明 Facebook page<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mCngMKb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmCngMKb.jpg&h=731f3c6e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4d781dee22d4378c289bf39c996abf1c33786a38","tid":1776282,"uid":27764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T12:06:19.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e779f9530dd871f6f788877e9e8d211c532f36ce","tid":1776282,"uid":27764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T12:07:54.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f733e34475adddbebc79557def3464d13fa8669e","tid":1776282,"uid":27764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T12:09:17.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/as